Name: unlock recent

Type: command

Syntax: unlock recent

Summary:
Sets the <lockRecent> <property> to false, allowing <card|cards> to be
added to the <recent cards|recent cards list>.

Introduced: 1.0

OS: mac, windows, linux, ios, android

Platforms: desktop, server, mobile

Example:
